  <section id="data">
    <h3>Data</h3>

    <p>
        DPV's data concepts can be used to indicate the use of any data, personal and non-personal. As such, they can be used as assets in ODRL policies. Furthermore, DPV's data source concepts can be used to refine asset collections and the personal data categories in the [[PD]] extension can also be used as constraints to refine party collections, e.g., by gender or age.
