  <section id="tech">
    <h3>Technologies</h3>

    <p>
        DPV's technology concepts can be used to indicate the use of any technology, including AI. As such, they can be used as assets in ODRL policies to define the conditions of usage of such resources. Furthermore, DPV's [[TECH]] and [[AI]] extensions include technological concepts that can also be used to further constraint rules within ODRL policies, e.g., a certain asset can only be used to train an AI model.
