  <section id="temporal">
    <h3>Duration & Frequency</h3>

    <p>
        DPV's duration and frequency concepts can be used to indicate how long a certain rule can be exercised and with what frequency, respectively. Furthermore, these DPV concepts have a close match with a few ODRL left operands. Such a relation is represented using the <code>skos:related</code> property, e.g., <code>dpv:Duration</code> has similarities with the <code>odrl:elapsedTime</code> left operand.
